# 2018.05.15
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Added "Topic", "Host", and "Participants" lines.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------


# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
EVENT::4.1::2018-05-16::19.43.41::PDT::Wed::EVENT::

Topic: 
